node.title: : State Highway 1 closed near ÅŒtaki after serious crash, delays expected
node.description: The incident occured between a truck and a car just before 6am on Monday.
node.content: ["A serious crash in the Horowhenua region has closed State Highway 1 with motorists warned to \"expect delays\".", "Emergency services were alerted to the crash between a truck and a car just before 6am on Monday.", "Waka Kotahi said the road is closed north of the South Manakau Road intersection with detours in place and motorists are being asked to follow directions of emergency services on site.", "The serious crash unit has been notified and police said an update on injuries will be provided when more is known.\u00a0", "\"The road is closed and motorists are advised to expect delays if travelling on SH1 this morning [Monday],\" police said.\u00a0"]
